{"tid":2131201,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［法律猜想］以李桂華既說法推論，如果一個國家不認同港國安法，不想國民因國安法被捕，可能需要禁止所有香港警員入境","createTime":"2020-07-29T16:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T20:07:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":192,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"4af5358971dace9ef07306786532878b3091c697","tid":2131201,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"1. 李桂華話，對喺外國犯國安法既人，香港警方都有&lsquo;管轄權&rsquo;，有權作出調查<br />\n<br />\n2. 國安法範圍係不限國籍(38條）<br />\n<br />\n3. 換言之，任何香港警員入境外國，都可能係去調查當地國民觸犯國安法既罪證<br />\n<br />\n4. 香港警方收集罪證後，或會因哩啲罪證作出拘捕；當然當地應該拉唔到，但當疑犯經中國、香港或其他仲引渡到地方，就拉得<br />\n<br />\n5. 因此，容許香港警察入境，會增加當地國民出境時因為國安法被忽然拘捕既風險<br />\n<br />\n6. 要避開哩個風險，唯有唔俾香港警察入境去調查<br />\n<br />\n7. 如果一個國家認同、接受香港國安法，當然唔需要咁做，否則就要考慮相應措施保護自己國民<br />\n<br />\nRef<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202444e/cs220202444136.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202444e%2Fcs220202444136.pdf&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=1a290286\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202444e/cs220202444136.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"9d70834e3ed78ddc90cd600c2e93d5e465468f67","tid":2131201,"uid":127929,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"首先要人地國家都認同黑警係有害既物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0680dff9f5fa91732f7e4b3f710926a388e1074a","tid":2131201,"uid":321059,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9d70834e3ed78ddc90cd600c2e93d5e465468f67","tid":2131201,"uid":127929,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"首先要人地國家都認同黑警係有害既物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"原來李桂華都係加速師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" cl